4. DEVELOPER ACCOUNTS
Relationship between Developer Accounts and Privacy Policy
This privacy policy applies specifically to apps published under the Light Thunder Apps and Purple Pillow Games developer accounts, both of which are managed by parent company Weewoo.
The Light Thunder Apps and Purple Pillow Games developer accounts are responsible for ensuring compliance with privacy regulations for apps published on Google Play. This policy covers all apps published under these accounts, indicating how user data is collected, used and protected.